snippet.title: "Kill the King" Showcase and Playtesting!
snippet.description:
https://quantumlionlabs.com/playtest/

"Kill the King" is a VR, multiplayer, physics-based, assassin game.

If you're interested in playtesting this and following its development, sign up here: 
https://quantumlionlabs.com/playtest/

You can also follow us on Twitter here: https://twitter.com/QuantumLionLabs
